            <p>Harmony is a Web App that lets you to record music virtually. Compose music at your liesure or listen to the ones recorded by other users!</p>
            <h2>How to use</h2>
            <p>You can use the keyboard or click on the keys displayed on the screen to play the particular note.</p>
            <p>Click on the Record button to record your music and click on it again to stop recording and listen to a preview. You can also listen to it using the Play button.</p>
            <p>If you wish to save the music, click on the save button, enter a title for your music and click on the Save button in the pop-up.</p>
